# =====================================
# iMak Trading Japan - Monorepo .gitignore
# Created: 2026-04-25
# =====================================

# === iMakCatalog runtime DB (2026-04-30) ===
# 並列セッション間で branch checkout すると sqlite blob が baseline に巻き戻り
# データロスする構造的問題を解消するため、本ファイルは git から除外する.
# 復旧不可能なロスト事故を 2026-04-29 に経験 (DW-6900/DW-5600 計 101 records 消失).
iMakCatalog/db/products.sqlite
iMakCatalog/db/*.sqlite-journal
iMakCatalog/db/*.sqlite-wal
iMakCatalog/db/*.sqlite-shm

# === SECRETS (must never be committed) ===
**/API key.txt
**/api_key.txt
**/ebay keys.txt
**/gemini_key.txt
**/groq_key.txt
**/openai_key.txt
**/anthropic_key.txt
**/credentials.json
**/service_account*.json
double-hold-*.json
*.pem
*.key

# === Python ===
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*$py.class
*.so
.Python
.pytest_cache/
.mypy_cache/
.ruff_cache/
.coverage
htmlcov/
.tox/

# === Virtual env ===
.venv/
venv/
env/

# === IDE ===
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo

# === OS ===
desktop.ini
Thumbs.db
.DS_Store
ehthumbs.db

# === Excel/Office temp ===
~$*.xlsx
~$*.xls
~$*.docx

# === Logs ===
*.log
psa_run_*.log
**/logs/

# === Cache files (regeneratable) ===
**/*_cache.json
**/cache/
**/data/*_cache.json
**/bandai_*_cache.json
**/pokemon_*_cache.json
**/psa_cache.json

# === Generated CSV outputs (regeneratable) ===
**/csv_output/*.csv
**/csv_output/*.json
**/ebay_upload_*.csv
**/tcg_upload_*.csv
**/tshirt_upload_*.csv
**/gshock_upload_*.csv
**/porter_upload_*.csv
**/ichibankuji_upload_*.csv

# === Review/audit logs (regeneratable) ===
**/review_logs/*.jsonl
**/review_logs/*.md
**/audit_logs/*.md

# === Sold data (large, regeneratable) ===
**/sold_data/*.xlsx
**/sold_data/*.csv

# === Misc temp/test outputs ===
**/_*.csv
**/scout_result.xlsx
**/tmp/
**/temp/
*.tmp

# Worktree marker (各 worktree のローカルファイル、git track しない)
.PROJECT_LOCKED.md

# === Claude Code session cache (各プロジェクト) ===
**/.claude/

# === Advisor 一時 decompile ===
iMakAdvisor/.decompile_tmp/

# === 個人 window geometry / settings ===
**/.window_geometry.json

# === 一時 scripts (アンダースコア始まり Python) ===
**/_*.py

# === decision logs (運用データ、再生成可) ===
**/decision_logs/

# === iMakHQ csv_output (運用データ、再生成可) ===
iMakHQ/csv_output/

# === iMakHQ rarara_reports (運用データ) ===
iMakHQ/rarara_reports/

# === 新 worktree (元 monorepo に古いスナップショット残る場合の保険) ===
# 注意: 新 worktree は別 path (C:/dev/iMak_inventory etc) で管理、元 monorepo の同名フォルダは古いものなので ignore
iMakInventory/
iMakHarvest/
